{
  "stem": "9245.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But by the same token, the bureaucrats, the bureaucrats, as the Germans are, they had a befehl, which means the command, that-- that you can only loot till midnight.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it has to stop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were looting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a-- it-- a-- a very awkward thing happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They caught a gentile fellow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was looting, and it was close to midnight or a little bit past midnight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They arrested him And they put him up together with the hostages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what-- my father was not among the hostages, by the way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going to happen to the hostages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they stayed three days, somewhere, in a-- in a separate house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put this gentile fellow, and they put him up together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After-- on the third day, they said something is-- something is happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took out the hostages, and they told them to dig a-- a hole, to dig like a grave, in the center of the city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody was sure that this is-- they're going to shoot the-- the 22 hostages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where they're going to bury them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that-- but that wasn't the case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They shot, in the open, in front of the entire city, they shot this gentile fellow for disobeying orders of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they buried him right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they let the 22 hostages go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But that wasn't the beginning of the picnic that we had with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the beginning of the real, horrible, atrocious, terrible life that we started experiencing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Every single day, they had all kind of announcements, put out on walls, put out on a-- on a electric poles, that the Jews had to dispose of, giveaway their silver, any gold, any jewelry.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had to give them away.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
